    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ad0beed5-6c08-cb4f-9825-c109cbd46f57"],
 " and the slice separations satisfy the bilocal scaling relation given in \
equation (3), the spatial component becomes"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987278963682211*^9, 
  3.9872789940993977`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f7a39fe0-fe7b-bf48-a3cd-\
ca3e0d3192ed"],

