   3.9800123717656384`*^9}, {3.9800125964760056`*^9, 3.980012596579132*^9}, {
   3.98001263550218*^9, 3.9800126362062607`*^9}, 3.9816598787058296`*^9, {
   3.9838750466517277`*^9, 3.983875047914116*^9}, {3.9874493032803802`*^9, 
   3.9874493548651276`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"28a14c1d-e982-4c42-b425-\
204e1e4c063b"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Global Acceleration Budget", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987490238200947*^9},ExpressionUUID->"b67e0ebb-f4c4-6248-a9ec-\
33b9b17e463d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The local closure fixes all non-homogeneous acceleration flux as sourced by \
inertial content. In the weak-field regime this reduces to baryonic mass. \
Integrating the flux law over the full homogeneous domain of scale ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["L", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$L$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "02526d2a-7a5e-7f46-bdd5-239af03a209c"],
 " gives"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987490249957735*^9, 
  3.987490258505226*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"18843d88-e785-954d-aecf-\
e19ad7ab9133"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox["\[CapitalPhi]", 
          StyleBox["tot", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         "\[ContourIntegral]", 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["a", FontSlant -> "Bold"], 
          StyleBox["conc", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[NegativeThinSpace]", 
         "\[CenterDot]", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["S", FontSlant -> "Bold"], "\[LongEqual]", "-4", "\[Pi]", 
         StyleBox["G", "TI"], 
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["M", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["b", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["tot", FontSlant -> "Plain"]]}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$\\Phi_{\\mathrm{tot}}=\\oint \\mathbf a_{\\mathrm{conc}}\\!\\cdot \
d\\mathbf S=-4\\pi G M_b^{\\mathrm{tot}}$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], " ", "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987490315463793*^9, 3.9874903208074226`*^9}, {
  3.987491717776163*^9, 
  3.9874917177841625`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0a06bac3-9420-264d-a0ef-\
9918fbcfca69"],

Cell["\<\
Using the global relation between baryonic mass and the background \
acceleration scale,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987490338219391*^9},ExpressionUUID->"b50bdea8-ba68-c040-950e-\
9352cf09ee20"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["M", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["b", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["tot", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
            SuperscriptBox[
             StyleBox["L", "TI"], "2"]}], 
          StyleBox["G", "TI"]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$M_b^{\\mathrm{tot}}=\\frac{A L^2}{G}$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874903477789783`*^9, 3.987490352360079*^9}, {
  3.987491725406622*^9, 
  3.987491725406622*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"28ae1850-6354-dc42-b907-\
d77389eb844f"],

Cell["yields", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987490363178322*^9},ExpressionUUID->"5a308995-1003-5544-96fb-\
7a3943571c18"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox["\[CapitalPhi]", 
          StyleBox["tot", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[LongEqual]", "-4", 
         "\[Pi]", 
         StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["L", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$\\Phi_{\\mathrm{tot}}=-4\\pi A L^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987490371295191*^9, 3.9874903764738293`*^9}, {
  3.9874917388113136`*^9, 
  3.9874917388113136`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f7ea962d-b134-ed4a-9634-\
085ac67ec96b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Thus the available concentration flux is fixed by the background scale ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$A$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c568705a-ba4b-be4e-8868-6198bc35f9dd"],
 " and is completely accounted for by baryonic mass. Local gravitational \
systems therefore correspond to partial redistributions of a finite \
acceleration budget, so gravitational collapse approaches a saturated \
configuration rather than an unbounded one."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.987490387778578*^9, 
  3.987490608594948*^9},ExpressionUUID->"57183458-3bb0-bb4f-96e6-\
71c62ce8119c"],

Cell[TextData[StyleBox["Mach\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Bucket", "Subsection"]], \
"Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874905173038464`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"9551930a-b0a6-e646-80ee-\
e2fc56a884b9"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The bilocal reduction introduces a homogeneous acceleration scale ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["A", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$A$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9f12e74f-108c-7f4d-90d8-480965488644"],
 " fixed by the geometry of the manifold. This acceleration is not sourced by \
baryonic matter; instead, baryonic mass redistributes it through conservation \
of acceleration flux (equation (30))."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987490530328121*^9, 3.9874905437427425`*^9}, {
  3.987490621318289*^9, 
  3.987490621452709*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8d2e8f2d-81b8-0c49-97ec-\
5d4b4951e807"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For a rotating system of radius ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["r", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$r$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "219239a9-42dd-e14a-894f-5ebad7832d12"],
 " and tangential speed ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["v", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$v$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "18b95f87-e776-f343-8627-7038556dfd63"],
 ", circular motion requires an inward centripetal acceleration ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["v", "TI"], "2"], "/", 
         StyleBox["r", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$v^{2}/r$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "dd382e71-055d-ce4a-aa0a-0e1f4a55afdf"],
 ". In this framework, that requirement is met by redistributing the \
background field to produce the necessary inward concentration."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874905562070503`*^9, 3.987490587255163*^9}, 
   3.987490629512892*^9},ExpressionUUID->"79ad2910-895c-5640-a00a-\
4c817d7107dc"],

Cell["\<\
Because the total acceleration is finite, this redistribution cannot be \
local: any concentration within the system must be balanced globally. \
Rotational inertia therefore depends on the global distribution of mass \
through the shared acceleration field, providing a Machian interpretation.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874905716815205`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"24ee3e63-01d3-a549-ae61-\
931a9c47e4b9"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Regularity of the Manifold", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874917869532585`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"e75e6e76-a56b-2046-89ff-\
2dac6566aef5"],

Cell["\<\
Because the manifold acceleration scale is finite, collapse approaches \
saturated configurations of finite density and radius rather than singular \
limits. The manifold accordingly remains smooth under the evolution defined \
by the geometry and does not admit singular collapse.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874918500659504`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"ec033e70-17a5-654f-8d15-\
01c69d946285"],

Cell["\<\
Causal ordering is fixed by the intrinsic geometry of allowable separations, \
not by any imposed signal speed. Only trajectories consistent with this \
ordering admit an operational time parameter, excluding closed timelike \
curves and the associated causal paradoxes.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987491858048662*^9},ExpressionUUID->"9e9a8a2c-4a5a-544e-869b-\
ef166e71f137"],

Cell["\<\
The causal structure and finite acceleration budget thereby avoid \
singularities and causal paradoxes.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987491865791519*^9},ExpressionUUID->"40d2bf16-c5ec-5645-bab5-\
65ebfeec1e6e"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Local Dynamics", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987491877111046*^9},ExpressionUUID->"53850a16-45e2-0b4e-9167-\
e7b040e9ccc1"],

Cell["\<\
Having established the gravitational and causal structure, we now define the \
operational dynamics governing motion within the manifold.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987491893391239*^9},ExpressionUUID->"a3bf4cfb-823e-c54c-ba7a-\
1b9a8523eadc"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Operational Time", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874919028459396`*^9, 
  3.987491904633089*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5b56b784-96d7-6145-b6dc-\
1208f34262f3"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Imposing the null condition ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"\[CapitalDelta]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["s", "TI"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$\\Delta s^2=0$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "74c3d810-5329-394c-b76d-b687a159ae45"],
 " on equation (25) gives"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.98749191425906*^9, 3.987491924839073*^9}, {
  3.98757854911339*^9, 
  3.9875785514545956`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"97b77db4-c15f-484f-b230-\
50658e482ddc"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "\[CapitalDelta]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["t", "TI"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", "\[CapitalDelta]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["x", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$(V_0 - At)^2 \\Delta t^2=\\Delta x^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987491935071209*^9, 3.9874919396011486`*^9}, {
  3.987692488702429*^9, 
  3.987692488702429*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2fced01b-731a-194d-85f0-\
5e02b4c96499"],

Cell["so that", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874919538063736`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"c710de00-fdc4-d647-9e04-\
4d339ab88e9d"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"\[CapitalDelta]", 
         StyleBox["t", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{"\[CapitalDelta]", 
            StyleBox["x", "TI"]}], 
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}]]}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$\\Delta t=\\frac{\\Delta x}{(V_0 - At)}$", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987491966165079*^9, 3.9874919704986153`*^9}, {
  3.9876924984872894`*^9, 
  3.987692498488325*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fb113a18-c738-bb4a-b002-\
60132c9da169"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "This defines the null boundary of the local geometry and fixes the relation \
between spatial separation and temporal increment through the scale ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"(", 
         RowBox[{
           SubscriptBox[
            StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
           StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
           StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$(V_0 - At)$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d20348d2-1228-c249-8a12-911aa997a740"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874919829161434`*^9, 
  3.9874919887001286`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"430e1d27-f7e2-894d-a6ce-\
e09ca9f8d406"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Observable time is defined operationally by null exchange between nearby \
worldlines. One tick of the clock is a complete round trip of a signal along \
null trajectories, and the temporal parameter ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["t", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$t$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8a8488cf-ffc9-7849-9ebb-ff9f8254653f"],
 " is identified with the number of such cycles, which defines an invariant \
ordering of events. The null relation ensures that each cycle corresponds to \
a fixed temporal increment set by the local scale ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"(", 
         RowBox[{
           SubscriptBox[
            StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
           StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
           StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$(V_0 - At)$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "283917b9-b9c4-0648-afcb-b9cbc42d4be0"],
 " and restricts admissible trajectories to those consistent with this \
ordering."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987492002298952*^9, 
  3.98749201943334*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"035da126-d093-1843-8f48-\
6a031bdcef84"],

Cell["\<\
The null relation therefore fixes the local causal structure and operational \
ordering of events. Observable motion and the invariant timelike interval \
both arise from this same local geometry, so causality, motion, and \
measurable duration are unified through the null structure of the manifold.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987519144264351*^9},ExpressionUUID->"a24803d5-366d-0648-ba69-\
e99a776786b4"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Proper Time", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874921219040546`*^9, 3.9874921277051716`*^9}, 
   3.9874922038936577`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"8482cf96-9afe-9e4e-904c-\
40ab4f6309e2"],

Cell["Using the local interval defined in equation (25),", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874922180436287`*^9, {3.9875134188959084`*^9, 3.987513424270832*^9}, {
   3.987579009752186*^9, 
   3.9875790100799465`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f69697a6-adda-d14d-92c6-\
e54d957294c2"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["s", "TI"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", "-", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["t", "TI"], "2"], "+", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["x", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$ds^2 = - (V_0 - At)^2 dt^2 + dx^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874922276323586`*^9, 3.9874922306187325`*^9}, {
  3.9876925158273563`*^9, 
  3.9876925158273563`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"81fd6319-124a-9a4c-9451-\
36a422555307"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "proper time defines the invariant timelike interval along admissible \
trajectories, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[Tau]", "2"], "\[Congruent]", "-", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["s", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$d\\tau^2 \\equiv -ds^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d764d0b5-2857-894f-b01e-f514d63ac07a"],
 ", so that"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9874922422289295`*^9, 3.9875134452183266`*^9, {3.9875134943258495`*^9, 
   3.987513528809801*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3fb67474-b159-b147-ba39-\
b877004a9332"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[Tau]", "2"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "\[DifferentialD]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["t", "TI"], "2"], "-", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["x", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$d\\tau^2 = (V_0 - At)^2\\,dt^2 - dx^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9874923221899796`*^9, 3.987492326664034*^9}, {
  3.987513552075386*^9, 3.987513555548807*^9}, {3.9876925264831047`*^9, 
  3.987692526490383*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fd685cbd-ebb3-054b-a481-\
defa94d2af95"],

Cell["giving", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987492338704111*^9, 3.9874923440107937`*^9}, 
   3.987513711279051*^9},ExpressionUUID->"1b821f43-b2cb-8f4c-8ff1-\
4cde721c9845"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], "\[Tau]", "\[LongEqual]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{
             SubscriptBox[
              StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
             StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], 
         SqrtBox[
          RowBox[{"1", "-", 
            FractionBox[
             SuperscriptBox[
              StyleBox["v", "TI"], "2"], 
             SuperscriptBox[
              RowBox[{"(", 
                RowBox[{
                  SubscriptBox[
                   StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
                  StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
                  StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"]]}]], " ", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["t", "TI"], ","}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> 
     "$d\\tau = (V_0 - At)\\sqrt{1 - \\frac{v^2}{(V_0 - At)^2}}\\;dt,$", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987492681353283*^9, 3.9874926851930447`*^9}, {
  3.987692539493164*^9, 
  3.9876925394958153`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a9e89a85-597c-cf47-b809-\
5d954074e611"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "where ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["v", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["x", "TI"], "/", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$v = dx/dt$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f1c12f63-8181-a146-ba63-ad13446af997"],
 ". "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987492788708103*^9, 3.987492793763281*^9}, {
   3.987513749638445*^9, 3.9875137877200108`*^9}, 
   3.9875143879280567`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"89d1225d-fabb-394c-8340-\
f2d14390446e"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Local Momentum", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.98752794104422*^9},ExpressionUUID->"ac2d16da-5495-eb49-a1f7-3602240a3a7d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "A non-zero manifold acceleration defines a global acceleration flux that \
selects a timelike direction. The local interval arises from the Euclidean \
bilocal scalar (equation(5)) with orthogonal temporal (imaginary) and spatial \
(real) components, so it resolves as projections of a tangent of fixed \
magnitude whose spatial and temporal components vary with orientation. In the \
homogeneous local limit, this orientation is represented by an angle ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Theta]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$\\theta$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d6aa689d-b203-de4e-84f0-2ccf8ca78acb"],
 " relative to the flux."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987527990765087*^9, 3.9875280154109097`*^9}, 
   3.9875798248304424`*^9, 
   3.987580367373785*^9},ExpressionUUID->"27971af4-9f45-bc44-8154-\
df161e1817c0"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Let ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], "\[Lambda]"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {},
      "input" -> "$d\\lambda$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "2864b7b8-a445-384b-882f-38c7f48a73c3"],
 " denote an increment of the underlying constant-magnitude tangent. \
Resolving the tangent via the local invariant (equation (25)), the orthogonal \
projections admit a representation in terms of an angle ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Theta]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$\\theta$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "07051a42-d45b-9147-bdfb-758b07b61aa1"],
 ", yielding"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875280278515053`*^9, 3.987528046891304*^9}, {
  3.98758039774214*^9, 
  3.9875803982055264`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5fed8144-4e92-c74a-aba0-\
b1f91da86681"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["x", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{
             SubscriptBox[
              StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
             StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "sin", "\[Theta]", 
         "\[DifferentialD]", "\[Lambda]", ",    ", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["t", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", "cos", "\[Theta]", 
         "\[DifferentialD]", "\[Lambda]"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> 
     "$dx = (V_0 - At)\\sin\\theta\\,d\\lambda,\\qquad dt = \
\\cos\\theta\\,d\\lambda$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875280581416817`*^9, 3.9875280611139164`*^9}, {
  3.98769256076486*^9, 
  3.98769256076486*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"af47b67d-429a-7341-91f1-\
5e7b19d8835b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Observable kinematics are defined with respect to the temporal parameter ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["t", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$t$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d760a1ee-2e43-994f-8b47-0dce61dd23dd"],
 ". In the homogeneous local limit, the measurable velocity may be expressed \
as"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875280883305054`*^9, 
  3.9875280935204697`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"eab6d4e1-dfba-e54a-94d5-\
0376d38b400c"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["v", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
            StyleBox["x", "TI"]}], 
          RowBox[{
            StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
            StyleBox["t", "TI"]}]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{
             SubscriptBox[
              StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
             StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "tan", "\[Theta]"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$v = \\frac{dx}{dt} = (V_0 - At)\\tan\\theta$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875281043569183`*^9, 3.9875281078736763`*^9}, {
  3.987692569230345*^9, 
  3.9876925692328014`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2ebf6399-a2b0-ca45-a544-\
d0eac061c97d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The null boundary is reached when ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["v", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
         StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$v = V_0 - At$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "5f3c12f8-1f7b-d843-91d1-93e8bd513b24"],
 ", which requires ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"tan", "\[Theta]", "\[LongEqual]", "1"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$\\tan\\theta = 1$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ab8e1532-5a20-cc45-a8c9-b783f2eeb6ef"],
 " and therefore ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"\[Theta]", "\[LongEqual]", "\[Pi]", "/", "4"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$\\theta = \\pi/4$", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8bf146f3-6e1d-d54c-9fdf-c809df4325ad"],
 ". Observable motion is accordingly restricted to the timelike domain ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"0", "\[LessEqual]", "\[Theta]", "<", "\[Pi]", "/", "4"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$0 \\le \\theta < \\pi/4$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "86571801-7f0a-9f4c-89ca-008da55c8f1a"],
 ". At this boundary, the underlying geometric structure remains well-defined \
through the orientation angle ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Theta]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$\\theta$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0bdfc1d6-7617-964f-904d-340acc1f004a"],
 ", but the kinematic description in terms of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["t", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$t$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ccd37742-f65e-0c4d-a44b-b512fc414bf6"],
 " ceases to apply. Beyond this limit, the projection geometry persists but \
no longer corresponds to observable motion; its continuation is defined in \
terms of phase evolution."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987528130740753*^9, 3.9875281588636074`*^9}, {
  3.9875833977159767`*^9, 3.987583415107481*^9}, {3.9875834948923206`*^9, 
  3.9875835437514744`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0588087a-747c-c64a-bb19-\
838be6dc1cbe"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "At this boundary, the underlying geometric structure remains well-defined \
through the orientation angle ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|
    "boxes" -> FormBox["\[Theta]", TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$\\theta$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b8ad1648-4adc-8940-9b33-abfe6b09adfd"],
 ", but the kinematic description in terms of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["t", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$t$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "12e0c12b-9840-a14c-87eb-ed2731a60af1"],
 " ceases to apply. Beyond this limit, the projection geometry persists but \
no longer corresponds to observable motion and is instead associated with \
phase."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875281659894295`*^9, 
  3.9875281783579197`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"25f1073e-a17f-2943-91ce-\
07f72de0fd33"],

Cell["Momentum is defined from the observable velocity,", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.987528189970579*^9, 
  3.9875835601393166`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"d870adb8-bd25-6f4f-9cbb-\
b0bdce351cb9"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["P", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["m", "TI"], " ", 
         StyleBox["v", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$P = m\\,v$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987528198453129*^9, 3.987528201319971*^9}, {
  3.987692582889494*^9, 
  3.9876925829051666`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"81d1c256-a1b0-7041-a11e-\
9e940a577622"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "and is the spatial projection of the geometric momentum scale ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["m", "TI"], "(", 
         RowBox[{
           SubscriptBox[
            StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
           StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
           StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$m(V_0-At)$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ea41d9e6-d012-e14e-b839-9077e82fda2e"],
 " with respect to the temporal parameter ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["t", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$t$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1b6e139a-9a26-6c49-8925-79a81b08e8f2"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875282095176888`*^9, 
  3.9875282187014523`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3683c042-6c01-7e43-9e97-\
e45a2ce3a6fc"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Local Action", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875282356118584`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"bcaa9ae3-7e71-f344-bb98-\
e383d694a445"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In the coincidence limit, the bilocal interval \
(equation~(\\ref{eq:local_interval})) defines a local tangent of fixed \
magnitude and an invariant interval ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["s", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$ds$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "49a824c4-066d-f343-9b0f-33fdbdf8e686"],
 " describing local manifold separation. Weighting this invariant separation \
by the tangent momentum scale"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875282470400124`*^9, 3.987528270669752*^9}, {
   3.987583590955696*^9, 3.9875835932847385`*^9}, 
   3.9877514740473423`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"bbe05f17-4afb-f448-bf14-\
02c7716b32b4"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[Congruent]", 
         StyleBox["m", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{
             SubscriptBox[
              StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
             StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {},
      "input" -> "$P_{\\mathrm{geom}} \\equiv m(V_0-At)$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987583606834553*^9, 3.987583610470991*^9}, {
  3.9876926026405354`*^9, 
  3.98769260264431*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ef26aea3-ce9b-e54d-885f-\
527371359cfa"],

Cell["defines the invariant geometric action increment,", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.98758362114258*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f83dcc6e-e00f-6c41-9484-6f2122467459"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["S", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[Congruent]", 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[DifferentialD]", 
         StyleBox["s", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$dS_{\\mathrm{geom}} \\equiv P_{\\mathrm{geom}}\\,ds$", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875845602526264`*^9, 3.9875845640798206`*^9}, {
  3.9876926111334667`*^9, 
  3.9876926111360626`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a8081d58-eefc-2a40-bc2c-\
da363c61a9a5"],

Cell["with quadratic form", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987584576446438*^9},ExpressionUUID->"90981553-001f-0447-b756-\
5020d799f121"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["S", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"], "2"], "\[DifferentialD]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["s", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$dS_{\\mathrm{geom}}^2 = P_{\\mathrm{geom}}^2\\,ds^2$", 
     "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987584633800102*^9, 3.9875846371423664`*^9}, {
  3.9876926248276653`*^9, 
  3.9876926248276653`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5af965f2-ea6e-e846-a2f8-\
703f004fc155"],

Cell["Using the local invariant", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987528336853121*^9},ExpressionUUID->"4e1e035f-e895-9543-a55d-\
e3de1400d5e4"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["s", "TI"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", "-", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["t", "TI"], "2"], "+", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["x", "TI"], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$ds^2 = - (V_0 - At)^2 dt^2 + dx^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987528345800127*^9, 3.9875283497795506`*^9}, {
  3.987692642954933*^9, 
  3.987692642954933*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4b28f217-0fb4-da4f-82dc-\
27876b321224"],

Cell["the action-space interval becomes", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.98752835749988*^9},ExpressionUUID->"17a6b614-d846-af4e-b392-b92318ea36ce"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["S", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["m", "TI"], "2"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], 
         RowBox[{"[", 
           RowBox[{"-", 
             SuperscriptBox[
              RowBox[{"(", 
                RowBox[{
                  SubscriptBox[
                   StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
                  StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
                  StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], 
             StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
             SuperscriptBox[
              StyleBox["t", "TI"], "2"], "+", 
             StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
             SuperscriptBox[
              StyleBox["x", "TI"], "2"]}], "]"}]}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$dS_{\\mathrm{geom}}^2 =m^2(V_0-At)^2\\left[-(V_0-At)^2 dt^2 + \
dx^2\\right]$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875283740944653`*^9, 3.98752837739937*^9}, {
  3.987693984705576*^9, 
  3.9876939847075806`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9cfb7f1b-3435-6d40-91ea-\
4b254bc7e69b"],

Cell["\<\
The temporal component defines the geometric energy scale associated with \
tangent evolution,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875283878759117`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"7dbad19a-1ba4-2e42-acfa-\
7c8f047caf66"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["E", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["t", "TI"], ")"}], "\[Congruent]", "-", 
         StyleBox["m", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$E_{\\mathrm{geom}}(t)\\equiv -m(V_0-At)^2$",
      "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987528399409256*^9, 3.9875284029822826`*^9}, {
  3.9876940070936184`*^9, 
  3.9876940070936184`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a3936ae9-0d0c-0d4b-abcb-\
299d3eadbd37"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "while the spatial component defines the corresponding geometric momentum \
scale, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["P", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["m", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{
             SubscriptBox[
              StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
             StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {},
      "input" -> "$P_{\\mathrm{geom}} = m(V_0-At)$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "40494fd1-5a3b-3d48-898a-59d8edf36117"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875284117245026`*^9, {3.9875850889254856`*^9, 
   3.9875850911823616`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"95033abc-9877-224c-b9c1-\
ed99e226f452"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Evaluating the local interval on the tangent direction shows that the \
fixed-magnitude tangent satisfies ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["s", "TI"], "/", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox["\[Lambda]", "2"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"]}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$ds/d\\lambda^2 = (V_0-At)^2$", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a33cb5df-7517-724f-b0e4-2489edd558df"],
 ", so that"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875284359991875`*^9, {3.987585107539934*^9, 
   3.987585120205328*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"09b9eb24-d1cf-2f40-9ed6-\
587c219d85ec"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["s", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{
             SubscriptBox[
              StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
             StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "\[DifferentialD]", "\[Lambda]"}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$ds=(V_0-At)\\,d\\lambda$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875284439891014`*^9, 3.9875284487586365`*^9}, {
  3.9876941336809063`*^9, 
  3.9876941336828423`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"74b610e1-4230-444e-80b8-\
564322cd5ab1"],

Cell["and therefore", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.987528457129078*^9, 
  3.9875851978785324`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f1c193b1-acaa-f64e-b77d-\
65c044de8117"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["S", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["m", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
              StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
              StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], ")"}], "2"], "\[DifferentialD]", 
         "\[Lambda]"}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$dS_{\\mathrm{geom}} = m(V_0-At)^2\\,d\\lambda$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987528467789097*^9, 3.9875284705095787`*^9}, {
  3.987694144531229*^9, 
  3.987694144531229*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d8642650-4613-7c46-908f-\
e3cbaa03e2f8"],

Cell["\<\
so that the invariant geometric action accumulates along the manifold tangent,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987528553318531*^9},ExpressionUUID->"9715a19a-51cc-0a4a-992c-\
4af27cb26223"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["S", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         "\[Integral]", 
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["S", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["geom", FontSlant -> "Plain"]]}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$S_{\\mathrm{geom}} = \\int dS_{\\mathrm{geom}}$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987528561018255*^9, 3.987528564341238*^9}, {
  3.98769416703158*^9, 
  3.9876941670474873`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0a1ff366-f376-314d-b6a2-\
aad2833fc747"],

Cell["\<\
Observable action is obtained by projection into the timelike sector,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987528575268446*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f52c3e66-48b9-a34f-b310-\
c2dd3fa65473"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["S", "TI"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         StyleBox["P", "TI"], "\[DifferentialD]", 
         StyleBox["x", "TI"], "-", 
         StyleBox["H", "TI"], "\[DifferentialD]", 
         StyleBox["t", "TI"]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$dS = P\\,dx - H\\,dt$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], ","}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875285848438797`*^9, 3.9875285867794056`*^9}, 
   3.987528683443531*^9, {3.987694175208643*^9, 
   3.987694175210884*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8365d341-e5aa-1440-860b-\
0655a97b6c36"],

Cell["\<\
which defines the canonical momentum and observable Hamiltonian. The \
observable action therefore plays the role of the Hamilton-Jacobi principal \
function, while the invariant geometric action remains well-defined across \
the full manifold.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875286939179134`*^9, 3.987528695685667*^9}, 
   3.987585260792532*^9},ExpressionUUID->"cf2b70be-9407-3c4c-8065-\
408a9108c1e5"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Phase Evolution", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875854369105873`*^9, 
  3.98758544471418*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"362a052a-8fdb-2545-b38b-\
82049cf3c2e8"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The projection-based kinematic description applies within the timelike \
sector, where the local invariant defines a real proper-time interval. At the \
null boundary, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], 
         SuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["s", "TI"], "2"], "\[LongEqual]", "0"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$ds^2=0$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "71049b62-a737-7b47-a936-db3669d85de4"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["d", "TI"], "\[Tau]", "\[Rule]", "0"}], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$d\\tau \\to 0$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ac425d53-7c41-d848-a31a-a721bd83d177"],
 ", marking the limit of observable timelike motion. Beyond this boundary, \
observable motion ceases, while the invariant geometric structure remains \
well-defined and the geometric action continues to accumulate along the \
manifold tangent."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987586865925045*^9, 3.987586882174885*^9}, {
  3.9876942065793896`*^9, 3.987694209249342*^9}, {3.987751485515068*^9, 
  3.9877514909976025`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4a1a3bbe-7033-d743-ac76-\
9715fdcc95b7"],

Cell["\<\
The continued evolution of this invariant scalar is represented as phase,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9875868910980415`*^9, 
  3.987694216811638*^9},ExpressionUUID->"20bd86a0-0191-7645-993b-\
8ce63a5ca7fc"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{"\[Phi]", "=", 
   FractionBox[
    SubscriptBox["S", "geom"], "\[HBar]"]}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875872093294106`*^9, 3.987587265295164*^9}, {
  3.987587532393181*^9, 
  3.987587532393181*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6b38a303-4fff-4e49-892a-\
9951c802f067"],

Cell["\<\
where \[HBar] sets the scale relating geometric action to phase. Because \
action has units of length within the present framework, \[HBar] acquires the \
interpretation of a minimum indivisible bilocal separation, a necessary \
structural feature of a geometry that does not admit infinitesimal \
separations.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987587549502035*^9, 3.987587631206154*^9}, {
   3.9875878200812454`*^9, 3.9875878217707767`*^9}, {3.9875890008467884`*^9, 
   3.987589029407776*^9}, 3.9875891735963173`*^9, 3.987589255312624*^9, 
   3.987589310614382*^9, {3.9876942367889214`*^9, 
   3.987694253711817*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5f12034f-72cd-b247-8d4e-\
befc6e856dad"],

Cell["\<\
Phase evolution therefore represents the continuation of invariant geometric \
evolution beyond the proper-time-parametrized sector, while the underlying \
manifold evolution remains continuous across the null boundary.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9876942684528313`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"c0dd07e4-2b50-ae49-9eed-\
f2a6865c4f86"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Late-Time Evolution", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875898941119385`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"87532bb3-3425-e844-82e2-\
879c15bf12a6"],

Cell["\<\
The distance-redshift relation derived from the bilocal interval predicts the \
late-time expansion history.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9875899051432133`*^9, 
  3.987704410659214*^9},ExpressionUUID->"d00c7285-904b-fb47-b167-\
49130c7f8262"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Type Ia Supernova Sample", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875901504874706`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"65386a4b-9e30-6e42-8b31-\
1add9f151f1b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "We use the Pantheon+ compilation of 1701 spectroscopically confirmed \
Type~Ia supernovae presented by Brout et~al. [",
 ButtonBox["2",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->"Brout2022"],
 "]. The publicly released Pantheon+SH0ES dataset provides the observed \
distance moduli ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       SubscriptBox["\[Mu]", 
        StyleBox["obs", FontSlant -> "Plain"]], TraditionalForm], 
     "errors" -> {}, "input" -> "$\\mu_{\\mathrm{obs}}$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d87a2d4b-d8a6-a844-a616-969ea216709e"],
 ", redshifts ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       StyleBox["z", "TI"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$z$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f223eda6-e868-d745-8487-8325bf45fe62"],
 ", and the full STAT+SYS covariance matrix for covariance-weighted ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       SuperscriptBox["\[Chi]", "2"], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$\\chi^2$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "544684a5-364e-ba46-b205-414f9940da67"],
 " inference. The distance moduli are absolutely calibrated through the SH0ES \
determination of the Type Ia absolute magnitude ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       SubscriptBox[
        StyleBox["M", "TI"], 
        StyleBox["B", "TI"]], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$M_B$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "5ed346a5-9d9f-484d-b314-c40442a8925f"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875901634721127`*^9, 3.9875902413182735`*^9}, {
  3.9877044559678936`*^9, 
  3.9877044560811386`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"77e1e8ac-fa11-a64a-9548-\
4eeac3ca0414"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Luminosity Distance", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.987590236041628*^9},ExpressionUUID->"65046c59-4293-bb41-b2cd-\
983a929a7cdc"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The spatial separation predicted by the manifold geometry is given by \
equation (17). The luminosity distance follows from the standard relation ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["D", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["L", "TI"]], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["z", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"1", "+", 
             StyleBox["z", "TI"]}], ")"}], 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["D", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["C", "TI"]], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["z", "TI"], ")"}]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> "$D_L(z) = (1+z)D_C(z)$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7652781b-940a-6544-aa53-95ddba02b0eb"],
 ". Substituting the spatial separation yields the corresponding analytic \
luminosity distance"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875902522406178`*^9, {3.9875904182834682`*^9, 3.987590424315544*^9}, {
   3.9877044713157635`*^9, 
   3.987704474858799*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"74d8f144-9c13-254b-ae79-\
8583b39d9755"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["D", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["L", "TI"]], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["z", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", "-", 
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            SubscriptBox[
             StyleBox["t", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["o", "TI"]], 
            RowBox[{"(", 
              RowBox[{
                StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
                SubscriptBox[
                 StyleBox["t", "TI"], 
                 StyleBox["o", "TI"]], "-", "2", 
                SubscriptBox[
                 StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"]}], ")"}], 
            StyleBox["z", "TI"], 
            RowBox[{"(", 
              RowBox[{"1", "+", 
                StyleBox["z", "TI"]}], ")"}]}], 
          RowBox[{"2", "+", 
            StyleBox["z", "TI"]}]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, 
     "input" -> 
     "$D_L(z) =-\\frac{t_o\\left(A t_o - 2V_0\\right) z(1+z)}{2+z}$", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987590425940689*^9, 3.9875904293771076`*^9}, {
  3.987704757441786*^9, 
  3.987704757443939*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b829d8d1-9b73-564e-83f4-\
a779eb604db5"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   InterpretationBox[
    SubscriptBox["D", "L"],
    $CellContext`pmeLuminousDistance], "[", 
   RowBox[{"z_", "?", "NumberQ"}], "]"}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{"1", "+", "z"}], ")"}], " ", 
   RowBox[{
    InterpretationBox[
     SubscriptBox["D", "C"],
     $CellContext`pmeComovingDistance], "[", "z", "]"}]}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9756148822038364`*^9, 3.9756149287926445`*^9}, 
   3.9756150165915337`*^9, 3.975779023951092*^9, {3.9764777315644665`*^9, 
   3.976477753863432*^9}, {3.976477786893942*^9, 3.976477822834305*^9}, {
   3.976703433855234*^9, 3.976703459502556*^9}, 3.976729069670578*^9, 
   3.976729918229561*^9, 3.976789541170233*^9, {3.9770432923814983`*^9, 
   3.9770433108355255`*^9}, {3.9770443352346764`*^9, 3.977044338477255*^9}, {
   3.9788939549805393`*^9, 3.9788939624573593`*^9}, {3.9792342902148247`*^9, 
   3.979234297013012*^9}, 3.97956086250766*^9, {3.9795902667987556`*^9, 
   3.979590271346197*^9}, 3.987590534820057*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "In[135]:=",ExpressionUUID->"f551b214-01ed-1543-945e-a58534a3540b"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FractionBox[
  RowBox[{
   InterpretationBox[
    SubscriptBox["t", "o"],
    $CellContext`observationTime], " ", 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"2", " ", 
      InterpretationBox[
       SubscriptBox["V", "0"],
       $CellContext`initialVelocity]}], "-", 
     RowBox[{"A", " ", 
      InterpretationBox[
       SubscriptBox["t", "o"],
       $CellContext`observationTime]}]}], ")"}], " ", "z", " ", 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{"1", "+", "z"}], ")"}]}], 
  RowBox[{"2", "+", "z"}]]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9877517963068504`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "Out[135]=",ExpressionUUID->"497272fe-d0a3-434a-bec1-8208955b1ca8"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Distance Modulus", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9756150200057755`*^9, 3.9756150225197773`*^9}, 
   3.977249452073448*^9},ExpressionUUID->"085f44bf-a227-ba47-a7c2-\
50c31d451769"],

Cell["\<\
Type Ia supernova observations are reported in terms of the distance modulus, \
which relates the observed luminosity distance to the measured brightness of \
each supernova,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9756150572188587`*^9, 3.9756150802758617`*^9}, {
  3.977138409634054*^9, 3.977138456663418*^9}, {3.9800156176111813`*^9, 
  3.980015621991213*^9}, {3.987590461752043*^9, 
  3.987590465128336*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4a2aec16-5b13-194c-883f-\
b89217747e36"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{"\[Mu]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           StyleBox["z", "TI"], ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", "5", 
         SubscriptBox["log", "10"], "\[NegativeThinSpace]", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
           FractionBox[
            RowBox[{
              SubscriptBox[
               StyleBox["D", "TI"], 
               StyleBox["L", "TI"]], "(", 
              StyleBox["z", "TI"], ")"}], 
            RowBox[{"10 ", 
              StyleBox["pc", FontSlant -> "Plain"]}]], ")"}]}], 
       TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$\\mu(z) = \
5\\log_{10}\\!\\left(\\frac{D_L(z)}{10\\,\\mathrm{pc}}\\right)$", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875904858315735`*^9, 3.9875904893567677`*^9}, {
  3.987704773333889*^9, 
  3.987704773333889*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8373ce3d-ac78-9c41-ae6d-\
6b4267cbbcde"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    InterpretationBox[
     SubscriptBox["\[Mu]", "pme"],
     $CellContext`pmePrediction], "[", 
    RowBox[{"z_", "?", "NumberQ"}], "]"}], "=", 
   RowBox[{"5", " ", 
    RowBox[{"Log10", "[", 
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{
       InterpretationBox[
        SubscriptBox["D", "L"],
        $CellContext`pmeLuminousDistance], "[", "z", "]"}], 
      RowBox[{"10", " ", "pc"}]], "]"}]}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.97567493311989*^9, 3.975674991439678*^9}, {
   3.975675040370949*^9, 3.975675042736862*^9}, {3.9757659652786617`*^9, 
   3.975765999165697*^9}, {3.9757752472219677`*^9, 3.9757752521546288`*^9}, {
   3.9757756057848167`*^9, 3.9757756160746517`*^9}, 3.975776018444931*^9, 
   3.975779018113083*^9, {3.9761356599507656`*^9, 3.976135666751663*^9}, {
   3.9764778418052235`*^9, 3.976477865214346*^9}, {3.976654517732378*^9, 
   3.976654519994087*^9}, {3.976703028253977*^9, 3.9767030495975666`*^9}, {
   3.9767034728967323`*^9, 3.9767035427841606`*^9}, {3.9769895440475883`*^9, 
   3.976989550736824*^9}, {3.976990421533886*^9, 3.9769904263619156`*^9}, 
   3.9770441282243767`*^9, {3.9773432163172894`*^9, 3.977343217964386*^9}, {
   3.9788939266068115`*^9, 3.9788939429008083`*^9}, {3.9788971705561047`*^9, 
   3.978897191192417*^9}, {3.9790731024983807`*^9, 3.9790731152113876`*^9}, {
   3.979073227922785*^9, 3.9790732436817265`*^9}, 3.9790733333985844`*^9, {
   3.979150807627651*^9, 3.9791508453881626`*^9}, {3.979203147721056*^9, 
   3.9792031504890327`*^9}, 3.9792033262449512`*^9, {3.9792226417463875`*^9, 
   3.979222646059801*^9}, {3.9792231055673275`*^9, 3.9792231072576237`*^9}, {
   3.979227056550789*^9, 3.979227072491892*^9}, 3.979234471671442*^9, 
   3.979235300437216*^9, {3.979560873034767*^9, 3.97956087420574*^9}, {
   3.979590275480562*^9, 3.9795902768515415`*^9}},
 CellLabel->
  "In[136]:=",ExpressionUUID->"6b080fd9-91ac-f441-9bf9-d4501618e561"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Manifold Kinematic Parameters", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875912284568653`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"ed6f13a6-9548-344a-8a24-\
53b3ee82a799"],

Cell["The local null scale at the observation epoch is", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9875912386323414`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"5c3c87ce-4d1a-7947-8a50-\
04aab1598ad0"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["o", "TI"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "-", 
         StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["t", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["o", "TI"]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$c_o = V_0 - A t_o$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987591248933983*^9, 3.9875912526342106`*^9}, {
  3.9877047889113293`*^9, 
  3.9877047889138374`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a945f121-5b58-7c4c-8ded-\
b766cd213cbc"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Operationally, photon exchange is used as a proxy for this local null \
scale, so the measured speed of light at the observation epoch determines ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       SubscriptBox[
        StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
        StyleBox["o", "TI"]], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$c_o$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "80025882-227d-1247-a639-fc243437ec1c"],
 ", fixing the integration constant,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875912626692276`*^9, 
  3.9875912686777496`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"883cd635-917c-974b-b45e-\
627afb40f82f"],

Cell[BoxData[
 FormBox[
  RowBox[{
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["V", "TI"], "0"], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["c", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["o", "TI"]], "+", 
         StyleBox["A", "TI"], 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox["t", "TI"], 
          StyleBox["o", "TI"]]}], TraditionalForm], "errors" -> {}, "input" -> 
     "$V_0 = c_o + A t_o$", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], "."}], 
  TraditionalForm]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9875912774978867`*^9, 3.9875912817546024`*^9}, {
  3.987704798873913*^9, 
  3.987704798873913*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c3fa8a9e-fc54-fd47-bd84-\
66d2b1af1238"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"velocity", "=", 
  RowBox[{"First", "[", 
   RowBox[{
    InterpretationBox[
     SubscriptBox["V", "0"],
     $CellContext`initialVelocity], "/.", "\[VeryThinSpace]", 
    RowBox[{"Solve", "[", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[ImaginaryI]"}], " ", "c"}], "\[Equal]", 
       RowBox[{"v", "[", 
        InterpretationBox[
         SubscriptBox["t", "o"],
         $CellContext`observationTime], "]"}]}], ",", 
      InterpretationBox[
       SubscriptBox["V", "0"],
       $CellContext`initialVelocity]}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.976655346344805*^9, 3.976655387457781*^9}, {
   3.9766554426250362`*^9, 3.9766554522083683`*^9}, {3.9766563500706463`*^9, 
   3.9766563511629086`*^9}, 3.97665659177771*^9, 3.9767026035427017`*^9, {
   3.9767029132598114`*^9, 3.9767029812680454`*^9}, {3.9767035952541847`*^9, 
   3.9767036366311073`*^9}, 3.9767050780787125`*^9, {3.9767058126444683`*^9, 
   3.976705856138441*^9}, 3.9767303970650024`*^9, 3.9767895620948753`*^9, {
   3.9767977461518307`*^9, 3.9767977514710407`*^9}, {3.976800573891983*^9, 
   3.976800581158655*^9}, {3.976829471303879*^9, 3.976829474799244*^9}, 
   3.97690017842774*^9, {3.976900825068634*^9, 3.976900860740717*^9}, {
   3.9769009132915745`*^9, 3.9769009732032337`*^9}, 3.9769019268575745`*^9, {
   3.9769019774186115`*^9, 3.9769020042152996`*^9}, {3.9769123058149433`*^9, 
   3.976912307981268*^9}, 3.977568615757782*^9, {3.977568844304741*^9, 
   3.9775688458888664`*^9}, {3.977569562957918*^9, 3.977569599143881*^9}, 
   3.9775698226207123`*^9, {3.978892045402359*^9, 3.9788920727662296`*^9}, {
   3.9788922983442993`*^9, 3.9788923039190216`*^9}, 3.9788936329993095`*^9, 
   3.9788989185349655`*^9, {3.9788990581551895`*^9, 3.9788990772784653`*^9}, {
   3.9788996732004795`*^9, 3.9788996763575096`*^9}, {3.978899784567589*^9, 
   3.9788998037884007`*^9}, {3.9790549044557457`*^9, 
   3.9790549337317524`*^9}, {3.9790550465164604`*^9, 
   3.9790550475243263`*^9}, {3.979061818253153*^9, 3.979061831903414*^9}, {
   3.97906282230266*^9, 3.979062826014471*^9}, 3.979071821207487*^9, {
